{"tid":272571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍核動力潛艇USS Cheyenne 明早駛入釜山港參與撤僑訓練","createTime":"2017-06-06T02:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T05:50:18.000Z","uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b8d9bc1611d35287c8ec69c5dbd4f5f9fdb44611","tid":272571,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T02:37:10.000Z","msg":"5/6/2017 23:09<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;南韓軍方消息人士透露, 美軍核動力潛艇夏延將於明日早上, 駛入釜山港, 參與撤僑訓練, 應付北韓威脅.<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;南韓傳媒說, 駐韓美軍陸軍最高指揮機構, 明日起至星期五, 會舉行訓練, 演習撤離居住南韓的美國人.<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;夏延號核潛艇, 曾參加過2003年的伊拉克軍事行動, 裝備射程達3100公里的戰斧式巡航導彈, 以及射程130公里的魚叉反艦導彈."},{"pid":"a22f2260d7c66b9b853d76bd02f48bd1f8791d2d","tid":272571,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T02:40:19.000Z","msg":"潛艇撤僑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c050e9d4847ff0ddd09dafa998c6dfc1c85f88","tid":272571,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T03:27:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c3aaa1b32ae0ae0b726812b307e79c4cb5466c3","tid":272571,"uid":75032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T03:27:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>潛艇撤僑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nwhy not?</blockquote><br />\n裝到幾多人？"},{"pid":"fde7cc0f012798c3ae6724cce8d2fa4fdb8eb3c7","tid":272571,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T03:29:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>潛艇撤僑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nwhy not?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 潛艇拎黎開路 水面艦先拎黎載人"},{"pid":"b2980891ef24553